Package: pycnogrid
Title: Pycnophylactic Interpolation to H3 Grids
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Christopher", "Higgins", , "cd.higgins@utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for pycnophylactic interpolation of polygon totals
    to discrete global grid systems while preserving mass. The initial release
    supports interpolation to H3 grids using duckh3, returning
    either H3 cell identifiers or simple feature geometries.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
